questionsAndAnswers.question: What do we need to start working?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
I'd need your WordPress hosting login and cPanel login credential to get started.
Also provide me with your reference website links or design and content of your website, including text, logo, images, videos, etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will website be responsive and mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: YES! Website will be responsive across all devices (smartphones, tablets, and desktops).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you customize or redesign an existing website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! I do redesign, customize, or fix errors in an existing website according to your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my WordPress website easily?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: DON'T WORRY !!! Don't need to be a technical person. I'll Design it in a way that you just need to drag and drop things to add or edit the content.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, of course. I provide unlimited revisions in every package because customer satisfaction is my top priority.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer customer support after completing the order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do offer 30 days of free support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I don't. But I would recommend companies providing the best domain and hosting services.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be SEO optimized?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will develop the website by following SEO best practices of Google.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide stock-free images to be used on the WordPress website?
Is it necessary to discuss the project before order placement?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I recommend it because What happens is sometimes clients are not technical and it causes problems. So, it would be good to talk before order to make requirements crystal clear to meet your expectations.
